race.description: Boxing Day Tickets On Sale Now Maiden Plate
race.comment: THE TORQUE XPRESS (5) has not raced since his debut over 1015m at Grafton when he settled too far back, well supported. He's trialled well there for his return and draws inside. In a sharp barn and is worth following up. LA BIANCA (9) debuts for the strong Michael Freedman stable and looked good in her latest trial at the Gold Coast. Draws to advantage, and a bold run is likely. POETIC ANGEL (7) also debuts for a smart stable and Mallyon sticking from the trial is a positive. She profiles well. VERY DEMURE (10) went well at Ipswich before the spell and looked in need of the first-up outing at the Sunshine Coast. She will be better for that and maps positively. Goes in at a big price.
